    <item>
      <title>独家：消息人士称，中国复星集团正探讨出售三亚亚特兰蒂斯豪华度假村</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-fosun-explores-sale-atlantis-sanya-luxury-resort-sources-say-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[三名知情人士表示，复星国际正寻求出售其位于中国南方的豪华度假村亚特兰蒂斯的全部或部分，作为减少债务努力的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/deals/chinas-fosun-explores-sale-atlantis-sanya-luxury-resort-sources-say-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 05:45:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>贝莱德认为印度和印度尼西亚具有广阔的投资机会</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/blackrock-sees-india-indonesia-promising-investment-opportunities-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国投资公司贝莱德亚太区研究主管周二表示，该公司认为印度和印度尼西亚是提供大量投资机会的两个亚太国家。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/asia/blackrock-sees-india-indonesia-promising-investment-opportunities-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 05:43:23 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国当局讨论允许现货比特币 ETF 的前景</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/technology/skorea-authorities-discuss-prospects-allowing-spot-bitcoin-etfs-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[金融监管机构负责人周二表示，韩国当局正在讨论是否允许在该国销售现货比特币交易所交易基金（ETF）。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/technology/skorea-authorities-discuss-prospects-allowing-spot-bitcoin-etfs-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:12:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>韩国和美国准备在大选前就国防费用进行早期谈判</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-united-states-prepare-early-talks-sharing-defence-costs-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[韩国和美国周二表示，已任命特使启动新一轮早期谈判，讨论如何分担美国驻韩部队的费用。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/south-korea-united-states-prepare-early-talks-sharing-defence-costs-2024-03-05/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 05 Mar 2024 04:06:26 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>越南总理预计本周升级与澳大利亚的关系</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-pm-expects-upgrade-ties-with-australia-this-week-2024-03-05/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[越南总理范明正周二表示，他期待越南和澳大利亚在访问澳大利亚期间宣布升级双边关系。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/world/asia-pacific/vietnam-pm-expects-upgrade-ties-with-australia-this-week-2024-03-05/</guid>
